        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Fig. 13. Phylogeny of Amazonspinther dalmata and related cheirodontine taxa, including †Megacheirodon unicus (tree length = 55, Consistency Index = 0.85, Retention Index = 0.91). Characters 6, 7, 8, 9, 10, 11, 12, 13, 14, 22, 23, 28, 32 and 37 were coded as missing in the data matrix for A. dalmata, and characters 1, 2, 15, 16, 17, 21, 24, 28, 31, 34, 35, 38, 39, 40, 41 and 43 were coded as missing in the data matrix for †M. unicus. Ambiguous optimizations in both A. dalmata and †M. unicus are shown according to ACCTRAN (above) or DELTRAN (below) optimizations." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4567183/files/figure.png" .

